ac-ae41-d7091d849590_1024x1024.jpeg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1328px) 100vw, 1328px\" /></p>\n<p>INGRID REAR DERAILLEUR RD1 $699 Available in SRAM, Campy, Shimano, MTB or road actuation, short to long cages.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1355\" height=\"904\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/48T10_02_1024x1024.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-208206\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/48T10_02_1024x1024.jpeg?w=1355&amp;quality=75 1355w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/48T10_02_1024x1024.jpeg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/48T10_02_1024x1024.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/48T10_02_1024x1024.jpeg?resize=1335,891&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/04/48T10_02_1024x1024.jpeg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1355px) 100vw, 1355px\" /></p>\n<p>INGRID 48T10 12 Speed Cassette $469 Available in 44, 46, 48, 11 or 12 speeds</p>\n<p>Due to the pandemic, many of these items are delayed, yet you can backorder it all at <a href=\"https://biciclista.us/collections/ingrid\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Biciclista USA</a>.</p>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"9110c85b4512d54f82a6b82c0d84217a68b78256817e02c6f519784bea578188","category":"Cycling"}